# TODOLIST API Documentation

toDoList is an API that allows users to manage their tasks by viewing, adding, editing and deleting tasks.

## Resource Collection [/todolist]

### List All Tasks [GET /api/tasks]
+ Request 

        {
            http://todolist.test/api/tasks
        }  

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 5,
                "name": "Holiday",
                "description": "Enjoy the holiday",
                "dueDate": "2018-01-07",
                "status": 0,
                "created_at": null,
                "updated_at": "2018-06-26 07:37:51"
            },
            {
                "id": 6,
                "name": "one",
                "description": "number one",
                "dueDate": "2018-06-01",
                "status": 0,
                "created_at": null,
                "updated_at": null
            },
            {
                "id": 7,
                "name": "icons",
                "description": "8-menu-30.png",
                "dueDate": "2018-06-07",
                "status": 0,
                "created_at": "2018-06-25 13:54:54",
                "updated_at": "2018-06-26 07:36:31"
